text: José Gutiérrez (born 12 October 1992) is a Venezuelan competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Venezuelan male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Venezuela Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Category:Sailors at the 2015 Pan American Games
